{
  "stem": "352.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He took-- I remember, I, I was holding on to my mother's hand and my sister.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we were dressed warm.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we went to his house, because it was at night, late in the evening.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we never came back to the house there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he took us in the wagon with horses.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we were-- and he said, put the children down.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And my mother was dressed as a, as a, as a, as a Polish peasant.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he was a policeman, so I don't know how he did it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Maybe he gave, he bribed some people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And my mother gave him the valuables that she could not take with her.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "She gave him the keys of the factory, and which he took over.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And she gave him the papers and everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And she signed over everything to him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And he smuggled us out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We, he brought us to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And from there, all I know that there were a lot of people already in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "All I know that I was always holding on to my sister.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We were sleeping in some barracks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And then another person took us from Warsaw till the border, again, in a wagon where we were laying down under the straw till the border, by this time till the border of Russia.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "By this time, because Germ-- the Russians occupied-- this was I don't know exactly what year.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "This was the Germans, the Germans had most of Poland.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And the Russians had eastern Poland that was on the border of Russia.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And this I remember, that my mother and my sis-- my sister, she was the one that was telling me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "To her, I was listening.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And she said, if you will cry or if [INAUDIBLE], she said, I'll kill you.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
